          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Alas, it’s pretty rare these days to come across a truly original gaming concept. Developed by the catchily named Super Awesome Hyper Dimensional Mega Team, and published by the might of Team17, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The Knight Witch ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "appears to be one such occurrence, however. A bullet-hell, deck-building experience, BUT set in a metroidvania style world? Well, that sounds darn exciting, doesn’t it?",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hOCd8cejIM",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6hOCd8cejIM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"The Knight Witch - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch\"></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "The Knight Witch - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch",
