          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "was a blast, it really was, and is also truly original. How many games can say that these days? The mish-mash of genres works on many levels but may also put off fans of some of the lesser-used genres on display here. But if you’re a bullet-hell fan, or just a fan of fun, beautiful, chaotic video games in general, then you won’t go far wrong with ",
